E. 60th Street, at and east of the N.E. corner of First Avenue. Shown are old tenements being torn down for new apartment house development. View 1 shows Nos. 403 to 417 E. 60th Street, where a new apartment house was later put up, seen on the right in view 2. View 2 shows No. 401 E. 60th Street (right), a corner tenement and Nos. 1104-1108 First Avenue (left), which are also coming down.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: August 5, 1929
View 2: Sept. 25, 1935
